messages.content:
Step-by-step reasoning:
- The user wants the Basement Bar Closet Halo light to turn on when the Main Thermostat changes its Mode property to Heat.
- This is a COS condition on the Main Thermostat's Mode property.
- Heat mode corresponds to enum value 1.
- The action is to send the On command (DON) to the Basement Bar Closet Halo device.

{
  "routine": {
    "name": "Turn on Basement Bar Closet Halo when Thermostat Heat Mode",
    "condition": {
      "==": {
        "device": "Main Thermostat - Main",
        "status": "Mode",
        "value": 1,
        "uom": "enum",
        "precision": 0
      }
    },
    "action": {
      "device": "Basement Bar Closet Halo",
      "command": "On",
      "parameters": []
    }
  }
}
